<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>DIAMONDLIFE&#8482; (BOSCH PIN SLIDE) DISC BRAKES For Vehicles Built Before June 3, 2002 - MAINTENANCE -
        ROTOR
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="0">
        <title>ROTOR</title>
        <para>Visually inspect rotor for scoring, warping, cracks, bluing or heat spots or other damage or defects. If
            signs of damage or defects are found, the rotor should be replaced. Refer to
            <hotlnk document="s040402_X0404003.xml" xrefid="x0404003">ROTOR AND WHEEL HUB ASSEMBLY, Remove
                <xref refid="x0404003"/>
            </hotlnk>
            and
            <hotlnk document="s040402_X0404014.xml" xrefid="x0404014">ROTOR AND WHEEL HUB ASSEMBLY, Install
                <xref refid="x0404014"/>
            </hotlnk>
            . Refer to GROUP 04 - BRAKES in the Master Service Manual for details pertaining to reconditioning rotors.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
